{"tid":990580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★瘋搶！派錢申請表僅預133萬份　餘下百萬人要返家自印","createTime":"2019-01-21T16:53:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T01:26:06.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"92e2c42dd8b349594a5e78748b65f2c73d5135d2","tid":990580,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T16:53:10.000Z","msg":"派錢申請表唔夠分，100萬人或要返屋企自行列印。各區民政諮詢中心今日(21日)出現關愛共享計劃申請表派罄的問題，最初以為只是局部地區發生。不過，在職家庭津貼辦事處今日回覆東網時稱，只印製了133萬份中英文版申請表，遠低於當局預計將有237萬名市民合資格申請的數字。換言之，餘下<span style=\"color: red;\">逾100萬市民可能要自行在家列印，或自備紙張到民政諮詢中心列印</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190121/bkn-20190121212000777-0121_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190121%2Fbkn-20190121212000777-0121_00822_001.html&d=hstmky6LSwSreej27EnG4ttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=345fd4df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190121/bkn-20190121212000777-0121_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"04814268633876087909e8e83ffbdfcb2bc226ce","tid":990580,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T16:53:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190121/photo/bkn-20190121212000777-0121_00822_001_03p.jpg?20190121215027\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190121%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190121212000777-0121_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20190121215027&h=2276617b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"211698fdab659deb26f376d26a356797de8b7130","tid":990580,"uid":141176,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T16:54:07.000Z","msg":"手持申請表<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d30156e7f1c4848a963e46435a8d114fbcd3d3a","tid":990580,"uid":15984,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T16:54:10.000Z","msg":"Carousell 賣緊$70 份"},{"pid":"4cc433ab7ec691d31f7c3c3972312a4d95fbf6f7","tid":990580,"uid